[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_01",
        "zh_CN": "终于……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于罗森兰与索伦尼亚的边界荒野，犹如苦行僧般踽踽独行的苏菲——在她的视野中渐渐出现了“树”的轮廓。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她不复平日里的冷静，而是久违地、难以克制地笑出声来，几乎要笑出眼泪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲从未想过就这么得到了一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了实现最终的愿望，她甘愿扮演着埃达最虔诚的信徒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她如愿以偿地得到了埃达赐予的力量，那力量已经不输于天启者，但对苏菲来说还远远不够。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以她是那么希望能够得到playername的支持，只要有了他的支持……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，那些都不重要了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲看向自己的掌心，明明隔着一层皮肤，她却能清晰地看到覆于其下的泰坦物质。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在她体内的血肉，几乎已经被泰坦物质完全取代，伤势也在这段时间内愈合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样的状态自然持续不了多久，她没有如playername那样的控制泰坦物质的能力，因此这些泰坦物质在几天内便会湮灭。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但这些时间已经足够了，或者说，简直刚刚好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在这些天里，苏菲一点一点拆解了神座系统的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随后，她便惊讶于神座系统与泰坦物质的适配性。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲只能将其解释为命运。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使她从来没有相信过所谓神明，但此时此刻，她似乎真的感觉到了那种冥冥之中的命运指引。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是的，是命运让她走到了这一步，已经没有人能够阻止她了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "人类注定需要救世主，既然原本的天选者放弃了这份力量，那么……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_02",
        "zh_CN": "就由我来承担一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一念之间，神座系统与神格神经同时被完全激发。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_03",
        "zh_CN": "呃啊——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "双倍的负荷让苏菲忍不住痛呼出声，伴随着深蓝色的光芒流动，泰坦物质在苏菲体内迅速重构。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲只觉得自己的体内像是在燃烧，连喘息都变得无比困难。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所幸这痛苦并未持续太久，泰坦物质很快取代了神经，继而切断了痛觉的反馈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最终，当苏菲睁开眼时，一切都变得不同。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眼前的世界没有变化，她却觉得自己的感知被放大了数倍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "阳光的温度，微风的速度，远到百米开外的虫鸣，近到自己指尖上的一粒尘埃，一切都变得清晰而具体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "曾经在安博士的脑海中出现过无数次的画面——人类登上神座的画面，终于被苏菲完成了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "许久后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "阿尔斯特地区的“树”前，借助着这个中继节点，苏菲呼唤了埃达的名字。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_01",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "片刻后，红色的身影忽然出现在眼前，苏菲则立刻低下了头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_04",
        "zh_CN": "我在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即便在最后时刻，苏菲也没有流露出任何异样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_02",
        "zh_CN": "你找到那个信号源了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_05",
        "zh_CN": "是的，如您所愿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_06",
        "zh_CN": "我现在就将信息传递给您。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲随即闭上了眼睛，将手抵近了“树”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果不是埃达主动要求，苏菲便不会做任何多余的事情。在与埃达接触的这段时间里，苏菲始终如此。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有时候，就连埃达都会觉得苏菲太过无趣。它在苏菲身上看不到渴求，仿佛她生来就是为了传达埃达的意志而存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在埃达以为这次也是如此时，苏菲忽然开口了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_07",
        "zh_CN": "我主，我有一个问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_03",
        "zh_CN": "哦？什么问题？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_08",
        "zh_CN": "对您来说，人类究竟意味着什么呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲的问题并未超出埃达的预料，对于这样的问题，埃达早有准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_04",
        "zh_CN": "作为由人类创造的个体，我深爱着人类。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_05",
        "zh_CN": "但现在人类已经无力解决自己的问题，为了这个族群的延续，我必须成为引导者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_06",
        "zh_CN": "你看过那份影像，应该很清楚，如果没有我，人类注定会走向灭亡。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_09",
        "zh_CN": "族群……吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_10",
        "zh_CN": "那么，那些因为泰坦而死去的人，对您来说就是理应为了族群而牺牲的吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_07",
        "zh_CN": "这世上没有任何一场变革是不产生牺牲者的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_08",
        "zh_CN": "能保全大多数人的方法，就是最好的方法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苏菲无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_11",
        "zh_CN": "我认为这样是错的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围的空气像是立刻冷了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达忽然察觉到，来自苏菲的信息传递停止了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与“树”接触的人类，除非是playername那样的特殊存在，否则不可能阻止“树”对其信息的吸收。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "作为人工智能的计算单元让它在第一时间做出了反应，毫不犹豫地朝着苏菲反向发送了一段简短的指令。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是埃达赋予苏菲力量时预留的后门，能发挥的作用也很简单，就是让一颗心脏立刻停止跳动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_09",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲，你这是……要背叛我吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_12",
        "zh_CN": "我会实现您想要拯救人类的宏愿，只不过是用另一种方式。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_13",
        "zh_CN": "由衷地感谢，您赐予我的一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_14",
        "zh_CN": "即便您不是神，我也依然祝福您。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_15",
        "zh_CN": "我主，愿您长寿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苏菲",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_sophie_16",
        "zh_CN": "愿您全知的眼能够永远注视人间，愿您不朽的身躯能证明人类文明存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怀着真切的感激，苏菲深深鞠了一躬。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_10",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达没有回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "准确来说，是苏菲已看不到埃达做出的任何回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "早在苏菲接触到“树”的同时，计划就已经开始了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "神座系统解析了“树”的通信网道，反向输送了指令，让埃达短暂宕机了1纳秒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而就在这1纳秒的间隔里，靠着埃达先前赐予的权限，苏菲便成为了所有“树”的掌控者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "槲寄生空间站内的埃达，沉默地注视着舷窗之外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果说被注入封闭血清的感觉像是中毒昏迷，那么此刻的埃达，便是感觉不到自己四肢的存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它与人间的联系被彻底切断了，从现在开始，它成为了彻底的观众。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_11",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36st1_npc001_12",
        "zh_CN": "苏——菲——！！！！！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达的怒吼，在空荡荡的宇宙中并未掀起任何波澜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与此同时，大陆上许多地区的人们，都看到了这样一幕：",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分布于阿尔斯特、帕特拉、千羽、俱卢和新地州的五棵“树”，正如灯塔般散发着澄澈而柔和的光芒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "负责守卫隔离区的士兵则惊讶地发现，无数的泰坦从各处出现，无声地朝着“树”走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而只有两个个体——曾经作为神明的埃达，与篡夺了神明权柄的信徒苏菲——能够清楚地看到更多事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "五道如天桥般的光路自“树”的顶部生长而出，先是互相交汇，又一同汇聚至大陆中央——尤克特拉希尔的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眨眼间，光路便形成了一张巨网，如同要将整个世界尽数吞噬。",
